parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, or become stuck in gear, leading to accidents, injuries, or strandings.
symptoms: The transmission fails while traveling
the gear becomes locked in drive
the vehicle is unable to shift out of gear
the vehicle vibrates while driving
the transmission light comes on in the dashboard
loud thumping noise from the transmission
the vehicle stalls.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Issues with the dipstick can cause the transmission to become defective, leading to premature wear, failure, or other transmission-related problems.
symptoms: The dipstick is faulty
the transmission becomes defective
the vehicle experiences vibration or stalls.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Driver's Side Seat Belt Retractor Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the driver's side seat belt retractor can cause the seat belt to malfunction, increasing the risk of injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The seat belt will not retract
the seat belt buckle fails to latch
the seat belt latch is broken
pieces of plastic fall into the latch.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the air conditioning system to produce cold air can cause discomfort and distraction while driving, potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: The air conditioning blows warm air instead of cold
the air conditioning does not cool the vehicle cabin
the air conditioning system is inoperative.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Inadequate repair by the dealership can lead to prolonged periods of discomfort and distraction while driving, potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: The problem persists after multiple visits to the dealership
the dealership is unable to diagnose or repair the issue
the dealership provides inadequate or incomplete repairs.
